{"tid":795514,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"作為90後,好睇唔起身邊嘅同事朋友","createTime":"2018-08-27T05:32:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-27T12:18:08.000Z","uid":178623,"like":10,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a587b8841c8d2e6ceb42e1f96e03455f3988770c","tid":795514,"uid":178623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T05:32:11.000Z","msg":"2014年,適逢雨傘革命<br />\n當年我重係一個中學生 身邊人都話要去旺角金鐘佔領幫手<br />\n係學校都霸課係操場坐 佢地當中有幾多個人唔係為左唔想上堂而去霸課 有幾多人真係真心支持真普選<br />\n到左今日,呢班人已經唔記得當年所謂嘅鴻心壯志<br />\n去左邊?一放假就狗沖返去大陸食探魚飲喜茶 話上面嘅街邊小食好平叫我一齊去<br />\n咀上說大陸人有幾唔好 而身體呢?好誠實咁去左幫大陸促進消費<br />\n<br />\n當年我係無參與過革命,但依刻都無令自己或香港陸化過"},{"pid":"6ccf63b266cc5a26f59e7ddbdaa6ee433e9b9f16","tid":795514,"uid":25108,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T05:33:40.000Z","msg":"霸課?"},{"pid":"d6701f1a11b99637a539834954e62507db81e5e2","tid":795514,"uid":122134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T05:33:42.000Z","msg":"佔中原來係革命?<br />\n我以為嘉年華"},{"pid":"8a65cade7defc52a6514d48d07dcb9d787c8adbc","tid":795514,"uid":4780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T05:33:49.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"96d017d81ab8bb2056894632bf748c1f423785a5","tid":795514,"uid":178623,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6ccf63b266cc5a26f59e7ddbdaa6ee433e9b9f16","tid":795514,"uid":25108,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T05:33:40.000Z","msg":"霸課?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T05:35:11.000Z","msg":"罷課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41981c17b55e8f55585294554a509a9b198793de","tid":795514,"uid":178623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6701f1a11b99637a539834954e62507db81e5e2","tid":795514,"uid":122134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T05:33:42.000Z","msg":"佔中原來係革命?<br />\n我以為嘉年華"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T05:36:56.000Z","msg":"佢地當年講到好偉大要落去幫手<br />\n幫到幾多得幾多<br />\n<br />\n落到去咪又係成班朋友係到玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f20370d279a470c8203a585c6923d03baa1fc3aa","tid":795514,"uid":24024,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T05:37:57.000Z","msg":"中二病到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85d9c848a0fd8a3a4e57c8e30c12a069fafa0383","tid":795514,"uid":33359,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T05:38:54.000Z","msg":"我都係<br />\n一聽到同事朋友話未食過百里香我就好睇唔起佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df3719b58f472b352c384dd300c5f8adc7fecec8","tid":795514,"uid":142082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T05:39:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bf1ed9ef4c1ac94c63b90c6f067dd3388e965ae4","tid":795514,"uid":106426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T05:40:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fc01f0374d5f7b9c052ee193183987a09495a137","tid":795514,"uid":87999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T05:43:45.000Z","msg":"低質觀點<br />\n低質論據"},{"pid":"b34ccf0c237926a234d2edf98dae6214ef5eb56d","tid":795514,"uid":25003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc01f0374d5f7b9c052ee193183987a09495a137","tid":795514,"uid":87999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T05:43:45.000Z","msg":"低質觀點<br />\n低質論據"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:29:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95b2f3149b9ebd6be221774b652ed5dad6878ed6","tid":795514,"uid":55,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:35:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"98598eb816738f6e77bed20200f5fa51558413fe","tid":795514,"uid":169662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T12:18:08.000Z","msg":"未見過大千世界"}]}